1
00:00:08,559 --> 00:00:09,114
Thank you,Wendy.
谢谢你, Wendy.

2
00:00:10,575 --> 00:00:12,287
Yes,we've had a very good year.
对, 我们这一年经营得很好.

3
00:00:12,829 --> 00:00:15,746
We've managed to control our costs,as you can see.
我们设法控制了成本, 正如您所看到的那样.

4
00:00:16,623 --> 00:00:18,655
They're actually down 7%.
成本实际下降了7%.

5
00:00:20,094 --> 00:00:22,483
Not bad.But of course you're expected to do that.
干得不错, 不过这是你们应该做到的.

6
00:00:28,130 --> 00:00:30,614
And we've changed our advertising.
我们也改变了广告的方式.

7
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,821
We think that's helped new business.
我们认为这促进了新的业务.

8
00:00:33,184 --> 00:00:36,611
New business has grown 10% since last January.
从去年1月开始,新业务增长了10%.

9
00:00:38,179 --> 00:00:38,645
Not bad.
干得不错.

10
00:00:40,832 --> 00:00:44,793
With the industry in its current state,I venture to say it's quite good.
考虑到这个行业目前的状况, 我冒昧说一句, 这已经很好了.

11
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:45,904
Here's your water,sir.
先生. 您的水.

12
00:00:51,058 --> 00:00:53,574
I'm not interestecd in the standard report,Anne.
我对这种常规报告不感兴趣, Anne.

13
00:00:54,531 --> 00:00:54,911
I can read.
我自己可以读.

14
00:00:57,945 --> 00:00:58,522
By all means.
那当然.

15
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:03,050
Is there anything else I can answer for you then?
还有什么别的问题需要我解答吗?

16
00:01:03,611 --> 00:01:05,229
I've heard about the programs,Anne.
我听说了那些项目, Anne.

17
00:01:06,143 --> 00:01:07,735
Employee groups,the marketing.
雇员小组和营销.

18
00:01:08,983 --> 00:01:10,679
And I want to know who's responsible.
我想知道是谁在负责.

19
00:01:15,916 --> 00:01:16,291
I see.
我明白了.

20
00:01:19,582 --> 00:01:21,428
We have many other hotels,you know.
你要知道,我们还有许多其他的饭店.

21
00:01:22,389 --> 00:01:25,890
And I want them all to do as well as this one.
我希望他们全部都能做得像这家一样好.


